{"tid":938782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女:伸入褲襠有所動作=自凟變態佬 揾人拉佢","createTime":"2018-12-12T14:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T14:55:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"01332de680bc8a45675bb8acb8277ec63006207d","tid":938782,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"香港嘅土地問題到底有幾嚴重，令到呢位哥哥仔公然喺港鐵站對住陌生女性做出猥褻行為？受害人盧小姐挺身而出舉報，癡漢仲苦苦哀求「畀次機會！」<br />\n<br />\n讀者盧小姐周一（10日）約咗朋友喺黃大仙食晚飯，去到閘口嗰陣盧小姐行埋一邊用手機搵緊路，「突然發覺有個人貼住我企，我行過啲，佢又行埋啲」。雖然當時係傍晚6點幾放工時間，但未至於企到人逼人，盧小姐抬頭見到一名男子望住自己，隻手伸入褲襠有所動作，由於癡漢揹住背包，盧小姐擔心佢有攻擊性武器於是走人，「佢追住我，隻手仲喺條褲入面」。<br />\n<br />\n盧小姐向港鐵職員求助，癡漢即時走落月台，職員陪盧小姐去月台捉人，「佢突然彈出黎，自我介紹『我叫陳XX』呀！」兩名港鐵職員將癡漢捉住，對方見衰咗即哀求「畀次機會吖！」警員到場後以公眾地方行為不檢拘捕該名姓陳（37歲）男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59023364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023364&d=D%2BlS2%2BkA0YQiF9CPsTU8cE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a629931d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023364&h=0c62bee2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181212/59023364</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181212/large/1544620446_d7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181212%2Flarge%2F1544620446_d7d9.jpg&h=48993750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有賓州是原罪"},{"pid":"c60b357216603a62a1132d6049074955269dc920","tid":938782,"uid":41508,"like":52,"dislike":5,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82dec4745d25479dd7e44cbdb7baf22ab1effcb4","tid":938782,"uid":29784,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:01:46.000Z","ms